实、可怕的念头时常出现在脑海。我还记得哈里如何安慰我。」 在被问及他的母亲会如何看待这些事情时，哈里说：「我想她会对事态的发展感到非常生气和悲伤。」 报道还称，梅根对奥普拉说，王室内部人员不仅没有在她遭受恶意流言攻击时保护她，反而为了保护他人而撒谎。 她说：「在我们结婚后，一切开始恶化。我才发现，我不仅没有得到保护，他们还会为了保护王室其他成员而撒谎。」 此前有报道称，梅根在婚礼前把凯特弄哭。她对此表示否认，并说这是她与媒体和王室之间关系的转折点。 梅根说：「事实恰恰相反。婚礼前几天，她（凯特）对一些事感到烦心——确实是关于婚礼花童的裙子——这件事让我哭了，真的伤害了我的感情。」 哈里说，梅根把他从王室生活的束缚中「拯救」了出来。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-81fcfafe6adee484752f83e63b585b17_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "93 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/448371194"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IpIup24yR2YogEAMaCDYxOTE3MDQ5INXCm4IGMCc4kwhADnIJNDQ4MzcxMTk0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1617923361.7005386", "card_id": "Q_453468442", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 2868}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价漫画《进击的巨人》第 139 话（最终话）？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "漫画《进击的巨人》正式完结，大家有什么想说的呢"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-e4f5538686f67784c09fecd0a1336072_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "92 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/453468442"}}, "attached_info": "ClYIpIup24yR2YogEAMaCDYzMDUwMjc3ILrKt4MGMMgBOKk0QA9yCTQ1MzQ2ODQ0MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA8gETCAESD2RvbWFpbl9vcGVyYXRvcg=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1617923361.7009726", "card_id": "Q_443835000", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 Windows 是用 C 语言编写的，却默认对文件大小写不敏感？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3a6d1dbe4bb9696d9a4c71d52bcb4fa9_720w.jpg?source=ba7200d9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "91 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/443835000"}}, "attac